OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780927878
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after two
OL,4,C'suspicious' items found
OL,6,FResidents have returned to their homes
OL,7,Fafter two "suspicious" items were
OL,8,Fdiscovered at two separate properties
OL,9,Fin the space of 24 hours.
OL,11,FPolice were initially called to Abram
OL,12,FClose, in Fallowfield, Manchester,
OL,13,Fshortly after 6:05pm on Saturday, 6
OL,14,FJune, following reports of a
OL,15,Fsuspicious item found in a front
OL,16,Fgarden.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
