PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780927878
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after two
OL,4,C'suspicious' items found
OL,6,FThe Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD)
OL,7,Fteam carried out an assessment at the
OL,8,Fscene, and around 20 nearby homes were
OL,9,Fadvised by officers to evacuate as a
OL,10,Fprecaution.
OL,12,FAs the investigation continued into
OL,13,FSunday, 7 June, a second suspicious
OL,14,Fitem was discovered outside a house on
OL,15,FRostherne Avenue at around 2:45pm.
OL,17,FThe police have said that the two
OL,18,Fincidents are connected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780927878
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after two
OL,4,C'suspicious' items found
OL,6,FAn army bomb disposal robot was
OL,7,Fpictured at the scene but police are
OL,8,Fyet to confirm what items were found.
OL,10,FNo arrests have been made at this
OL,11,Fstage, and enquiries are ongoing.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Peter
OL,14,FMorley, of Greater Manchester Police,
OL,15,Freassured the local community that
OL,16,Fthere is no wider threat.
OL,18,F"Incidents such as these are likely to
OL,19,Fcause alarm in the local community,
OL,20,Fbut please be reassured that there is
OL,21,Fno wider threat", DCI Morley said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780927878
OL,3,CResidents evacuated after two
OL,4,C'suspicious' items found
OL,6,F"Officers will be on hand to ensure
OL,7,Fthe safety of people in the nearby
OL,8,Farea ` please speak to them if you
OL,9,Fhave any concerns."
OL,11,FDCI Morley added that it is "vital"
OL,12,Fthat anyone with information comes
OL,13,Fforward to assist the investigation.
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police have
OL,16,Fconfirmed the incident is not terror-
OL,17,Frelated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
